title: 6 Chess Books - April 2016 (gnv64)
description:
Here is a collection of 5 chess books & 1 magazine:

1. British Chess Magazine - April 2016
2. Chess Skill in Man and Machine by Peter W. Frey
3. Liquidation on the Chess Board by GM Joel Benjamin (ePUB)
4. Mastering Tactical Ideas by IM Nikolay Minev
5. The Blackmar-Diemer Gambit by Christoph Scheerer
6. The Tarrasch Formula by GM Sam Palatnik, NM Mark Ishee
